attributes.review: it is unbelievable what he is doing 🤦🏽‍♀️i just wanted the app to see what Mr.Cheeto was doing ❤️ but i couldn't get passed the first page. Maybe it was because i opened the app on a full stomach but i threw up😬So my mom came over snd asked what i was doing and i showed her my phone. She started throwing up. We were both so confused on what was going on because we don’t get sick to our stomach that fast. So after that i deleted the app👏🏽. But when i deleted the app my phone was acting weird. It would lag really bad to the point I started to see Mr.Cheeto on my screen! I thought well maybe its nothing until he took over my screen. So i threw my phone off a cliff and everything started working better again. I think he should make this app better so people like me can get passed the first page without going through all that trauma(stan the damelio’s for clear skin😚)

I was disgusted, this Cheeto Puff wanted my number for some reason, why? I didn’t give him the number. I’m glad I didn’t. But soon after I started seeing that Cheeto everywhere I went, and obviously I felt like throwing up! 😍😍😍. I don’t know how to make this stop, but it’s okay. Anyways what I’m tryna say is, Naruto 2020. Don’t be shy vote for Naruto. 😼😼😼😼😼. Remember kids, don’t trust Cheeto Puffs 😸
